    question: "How much tax can I save with a 3rd pillar?",
    answer: "Tax savings vary based on your income, marital status, and canton of residence. Annual savings typically range from CHF 1,500-2,500 for middle-income individuals, CHF 2,500-3,500 for higher-income individuals, and CHF 3,000-7,000 for self-employed persons without a 2nd pillar."
  },
