    question: "When can I withdraw my 3rd pillar funds?",
    answer: "Regular withdrawal is possible 5 years before or after reaching AHV retirement age. Early withdrawal is allowed for: buying your primary residence, starting a business, moving abroad permanently, switching to self-employment, or if you qualify for a full disability pension."
  },
