              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Employed (with 2nd pillar):</strong> CHF 7,056/year maximum</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>Self-employed (no 2nd pillar):</strong> Up to CHF 35,280/year (20% of income)</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Contributions are 100% tax-deductible from taxable income</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Tax savings: CHF 1,500-3,000/year for typical earners</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Investment Options & Withdrawal</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>3a:</strong> Bank accounts or insurance policies (tax-optimized)</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> <strong>3b:</strong> Unrestricted savings, any investment type</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Early withdrawal: Property purchase, emigration, self-employment</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Regular withdrawal: 5 years before retirement age</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm">
